Metabolic syndrome and C reactive protein in patients undergoing angiography: 
Inevitable association?

Barbalho SM(1), Bechara MD(2), Tofano RJ(2), Quesada K(2), Mendes CG(2), Oshiiwa 
M(3).

Author information:
(1)Department of Biochemistry and Cellular Biology - Medical School of Marília - 
UNIMAR, Av. Higino Muzzi Filho 1001, Marília, São Paulo, Brazil; Food and 
Technology School of Marília (FATEC), São Paulo, Brazil; Cardiac Surgery Unit 
